        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[💬👤 #地图帝: 🔗 热河行宫还在，热河省哪去了？]]></title>
            <link><![CDATA[http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1ODM5NjAxMQ==&amp;amp;mid=2247530950&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=7e24bed952d9577da2669305c67eb6a6&amp;amp;chksm=fd1d71cbb37073594380ddf3b5e0d3c0511273e463720f727c38fa0c9d1bd58a96b89c7025c7&amp;amp;scene=0&amp;amp;xtrack=1#rd]]></link>
            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            热河行宫还在，热河省哪去了？          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                                                                    <span role="link" tabindex="0" id="js_author_name" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta_link weui-wa-hotarea" datarewardsn="" datatimestamp="" datacanreward="0">地图弟</span>                                                                            </span>                                                                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                地图帝              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">地图帝</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">dtdmap</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">左图右史，历史地理不分家。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <span id="meta_content_hide_info">              <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>              <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true">发表于</span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                          </span>          </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><span style="font-size: 18px;">上世纪三四十年代，我国有一个热河省，它哪儿去了呢？我们从<span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;">承德避暑山庄说起。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100047295" data-ratio="1.2305555555555556" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFiaick4MbNqvuibK5Hc6A9H8H9Ovpq9KwRed4DeP8PgnTiaungFPqCHib7IlYGOWlK5ANbEQnOGrWf2GaQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">承德避暑山庄又称“热河行宫”，是清朝前、中期皇帝夏季避暑和处理政务的场所。避暑山庄位于河北省承德市中心北部，武烈河西岸一带狭长的谷地上，总面积约564万平方米，由众多宫殿、楼阁、亭榭等组成建筑群。山庄周边宫墙高3米，长10公里，称“小长城”。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100047297" data-ratio="0.975" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFiaick4MbNqvuibK5Hc6A9H8H97Ns8wnhc2Ea2NpSJXNDicheN4pQWA2S2rfLzz4GSpDjbVDjM9ia2m1Kw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1000" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;">避暑山庄主要分宫殿区和苑景区两部分，苑景东南多水，西北多山，又分为湖泊区、平原区和山峦区，利用了原有的自然山水，吸收江南、塞北之风光，不以皇家建筑辉煌取胜，而是以表现天然山水见胜的宫苑。是中国现存面积最大的皇家园林。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100047290" data-ratio="0.9212962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFiaick4MbNqvuibK5Hc6A9H8H9rRgNVZzcXdVZtunv7npjPXfXRQIicTXxn550BSatrqFaD7licG9Tjyiaw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">1703年（康熙四十二年），始建避暑山庄，进行了大规模的扩建。清朝皇帝喜欢待在热河行宫，康熙乾隆这爷俩在位总时间约120年，有一半以上的时间在热河行宫；嘉庆和咸丰这爷俩都是在热河驾崩的。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100047291" data-ratio="1.450925925925926" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFiaick4MbNqvuibK5Hc6A9H8H9Xzhu8FXWuLecsyKl1EcXl48OP5S0DqpIK8H272XS0SjicBQ1BKODiaSg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">承德避暑山庄湖区东北角有数十个温泉眼，即使在零下20度的寒冷冬季，水温也能达到8度以上，从不结冰。清澈的泉水从地下涌出，流经澄湖、如意湖、上湖、下湖，自银湖南部的五孔闸流出，汇入武烈河。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100047289" data-ratio="1.5" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFiaick4MbNqvuibK5Hc6A9H8H9eKfcw7tb0k87y1z4DIC52DNfbQN28bNWM3Z4hI9IcgtpEmqubUicFoQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">武烈河中上游因有温泉注入，冬天不结冰，又称热河。武烈河是滦河支流，发源于燕山山脉七老图山支脉南侧的围场县道至沟，在承德市大石庙镇雹神庙村汇入滦河，长约114千米。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">热河省已经取消了，热河始终存在。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100047296" data-ratio="0.7046296296296296" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFiaick4MbNqvuibK5Hc6A9H8H9l1AklMLbLC1P7kOlbR5HibgkBa2v43jkmib8x1VTIe0ic8kd4YIG5COEw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">1928年，先后设立了热河省、察哈尔省、绥远省、宁夏省，称为塞北四省。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100047298" data-ratio="0.6518518518518519" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFiaick4MbNqvuibK5Hc6A9H8H96MZ09sUxE5rkicDMMChuGuIMiaU97l4mJefEU0XAseRZNKeoNyqAkuJQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">有人说现在东北除了黑龙江省、吉林省、辽宁省，如果有个热河省就完美了，合称东四省。当时的热河省地处燕山山脉东部，北接大兴安岭，省会承德。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100047299" data-ratio="1.1425925925925926" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFiaick4MbNqvuibK5Hc6A9H8H9dUu1lc0cYhfu2oea1NbvGjvhwPCeJ1gO0koCsTFnDyibKaEw0Zibl7xQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">1950年代，察哈尔省、绥远省、宁夏省、热河省先后撤销，塞北四省大部分辖区并入内蒙古自治区。热河省一分为三，赤峰等地并入内蒙古自治区，承德等地并入河北省，朝阳等地并入辽宁省。</span></p><p><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;'>文：姜狼，著《五代十国风云录》《三国原来是这样》《血溅江东》《五朝宰相》《逐鹿天下》《柴荣是个好皇帝》等二十余部历史书籍，欢迎转载。</span></p><section class="mp_profile_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-profile class="js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe" data-pluginname="mpprofile" data-id="MzU1ODM5NjAxMQ==" data-headimg="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UJLOdsjrZFgmCIpN5LnSBfL46YhOGnNx4LP0utHmFvYohJJAicribSAwraG4EzVKriaszUFicrGF79ib06mu9SqKaxA/0?wx_fmt=png" data-nickname="地图帝" data-alias="dtdmap" data-signature="左图右史，历史地理不分家。" data-from="0" data-is_biz_ban="0"></mp-common-profile></section><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="1341457840" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>                              </div>    </div>]]></description>
